@Auth.Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5132

### GET auth challenge nonce
GET {{Auth.Api_HostAddress}}/auth/nonce
Accept: application/json

### POST verify SIWE (replace message and signature)
POST {{Auth.Api_HostAddress}}/auth/verify
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "<SIWE payload>",
  "signature": "0x..."
}
